headline: Wheel of Fortune LIVE!® Kicking off 2025 U.S. Tour With Extended Engagement at Paris Las Vegas
summary: LAS VEGAS, April 23, 2025--Sony Pictures Television and Right Angle Entertainment have announced that Wheel of Fortune LIVE!® will be hitting the Vegas Strip with an extended engagement at the Paris Las Vegas starting July 11. Hosted by actor, television personality and game show host Mark L. Walberg, everyone’s favorite TV game show will come to life LIVE on stage giving fans the chance to spin the famous Wheel, solve puzzles and win fantastic prizes!
